text: Workers at a state health department warehouse in Tumwater expected to receive a large shipment of nasal swabs to help expand coronavirus testing in Washington. Instead, they received hundreds of boxes  packed with what appeared to be thousands of Q-tips. https://t.co/4N5h7jjx3I
